## üèóÔ∏è Architecture

```
Your Input ‚Üí Working Memory ‚Üí Cache ‚Üí Checkpoints ‚Üí Long-term Storage
             0.04ms          0.08ms   0.7ms        Permanent
```

Four-layer memory system optimized for speed and relevance.

